page.title: 10People of Sedgley
page.content: {People}in{Sedgley}are quite boring sometimes,they don't like fun or having a laugh they only enjoy peaceful places.I don't know many people who are very tall.Sedgley isn't as big as someplaces so a lot of{ {gossip}goes around. Everyone knows each other and everyone's always friendly except some{gangs}of kids. In the main parts of Sedgley, in the Bullring there is a lot of noise and that is where most things happens. Sedgley children are doing many activites for{schools}as well. People in{Sedgley}are quite different from other people in other places.
